~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : smail                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : smail <user> [<message>] 
              or smail <user>@<service> [<message>]

   You can send mail to a remote service/talker if your talker is 
   currently connected to it.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : rmail, dmail, from, copyto
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
